crew1.title: Supply Officer
crew1.description: Provides supplies for the Nautilus crew no matter what the circumstance may be or call for. Officer Crumpton is there to lend a hand.

crew3.title: Lead Engineer
crew3.description: Officer Rawlins is the Nautilus' leading engineer and handles all the mechanical fixes that are needed.

crew4.title: Operations Officer
crew4.description: Officer Simon handles the operations and coordinates with Cptn Korte on the Nautilus' future destinations.

crew5.title: Executive Officer
crew5.description: The Nautilus' second in command, Officer Johnson makes sure that the Nautilus is running strong. He remains ready to take up command in the event that Cptn Korte can no longer do so.
